Download and parse the SEC's recent filings feed:

{% raw %}

secMostRecentListUrl[source]

secMostRecentListUrl(count=100)

Returns the URL for the SEC's atom-format feed of most recent filings.

{% endraw %} {% raw %}

printXmlParseWarning[source]

printXmlParseWarning(msg, el)

{% endraw %} {% raw %}

getRecentChunk[source]

getRecentChunk(count=100)

Parses the SEC's atom-format feed of most recent filings and returns a list of tuples: [(fileDate, cikName, accNo, formType, cik), ... ] with the most recent filings first

{% endraw %} {% raw %}
